{"type": "article", "id": 23075, "title": "这家咖啡吧看起来活泼，天花板上的灯帮了不少忙", "description": "以弧形柜台为轴线，划分了面包房和用餐区，公共空间和厨房。\r\n", "date": "2016-03-02T08:00:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3967, "name": "餐厅"}, {"id": 12974, "name": "布拉格"}, {"id": 24205, "name": "Café Záhorský"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 164, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021406146PIuqlpwMHix5Ej3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>似乎布拉格的零售店格外喜欢在白色的空间里搭配黑色的细金属或电线。我们曾经报道过 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/17609.html\">Showroom. 买手店</a>和<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/22107.html\">“proti proudu bistro”咖啡馆</a>，黑色的线条连接了白色的整体空间，给人干净简洁的感受和淡淡的工业感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406053udV0Dpv4Bc58ths.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Showroom.</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140606k3i9EZhqeWs1jfXD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">proti proudu bistro</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>在布拉格 Dejvicka 和 Eliasova 街道的转角的餐厅 <a href=\"http://www.cafezahorsky.cz\">Café Záhorský</a> 也有这种似曾相识，除一面墙是深灰色外，室内大部分空间是白色的。黑色的吊灯带着长长的弧形电线曲线随意地穿插，并没有特定的规则，室内家具围绕黑、白、红和原木色四种颜色，显得清爽极简。不过，你仍然能从彩色圆圈的墙纸上和自由穿插的电线中看到一份活泼和灵动，兼具设计感和趣味。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140606XPE8ObhGRgKBJHvo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140607u2AHyONpfxPGLnBd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>这里原本是一幢修建于 1929 年的新艺术主义风格建筑，沿着大概 70° 转角的街道而建，新建后依然能看到优雅而古典的痕迹。</p>\n<p>室内设计强调了这个特殊的转角，公共区域的墙面与外墙平行。大门正对着圆弧的柜台，贴合了建筑的形状，也将空间划分为多个部分。比如大门右侧弧形柜台延续到深处，是一个售卖面包的地方，配有少量靠墙座位。左侧是集中的用餐空间，柜台提供咖啡和酒水。</p>\n<p class=\"\">另外，在弧形柜台后面的墙壁是深灰色的，它的后面就是厨房和洗手间。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140608sS3j4IDrPUwbgC6Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">室外</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406083QMPXtE5BA9kjTed.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">弧形柜台</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140609moAYIWV8L5akdM2l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">面包坊</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140609h6n4FWHfL3tEzM9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">面包坊</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140610v9JMj3GICHc6mEqh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">餐厅</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406109I7R0crVX1CFTiZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33511348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">餐厅</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">至于这些有趣的吊灯，它们来自法国著名设计组合 Bouroullec 兄弟的 AIM 吊灯，而墙纸则来自意大利工作室 London Art 。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140611zvyV6RUlZSnJo70c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33511348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140612d4CBjbo5gMXYGz8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140612rhEU7GSKw81L5P2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140613LB8wChZqUj2xza1t.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"dragged\" style=\"height: 250px; width: 375px; left: 593px; top: 6849px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140613zpFh4Q18ofOnJmyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214061428VQZK5bmzulR0pC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/782437/cafe-bistro-bakery-zahorsky-jra-jarouseochovrchitekti\"> archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.cafezahorsky.cz\">Café Záhorský</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n\n"}